Constant active_raw: u8 be 1.

Enum Mode backed by u8 has idle be 0; active be active_raw.

Constant default_mode: Mode be Mode.active.

Constant default_value: u8 be default_mode as u8.

Check default_mode is equal to Mode.active.

Check default_value is equal to active_raw.

To main, giving i32.
Give default_value as i32.
